      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, making it an excellent choice for a dependable daily driver. While the exterior paint retains a nice gloss, you may find some minor rock chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful use. The interior is clean and comfortable, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Overall, it\u2019s a solid, honest car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
