    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, always kept it garaged and serviced right on time. It drives like a total dream and is looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. You really won't find one in better condition! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
