    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to list this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it still looks and smells like it just left the showroom! It's been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019ve been looking for that perfect ride that\u2019s basically brand new, this is the one for you. I\u2019m really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it. Come check it out\u2014you won't find another one this clean!",
      "price": 46500.0,
