    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated precision. Featuring the 3.6L MA102 flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), this unit delivers linear power delivery across the entire rev range. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, short-throw engagement, paired with a mechanical limited-slip differential for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis is bolstered by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), maintaining composure under high lateral loads while preserving damping compliance. This example is in concours-level condition, exhibiting zero bore scoring and a pristine undercarriage. Recent service includes a full fluid flush and a comprehensive DME overrev report showing no excursions beyond Range 1.",
